title: Nebula Fighter Full Version CD-ROM English
description:
Hi to all,


I share with you a classic arcade space shooter game in which you fly through asteroid fields and waves of enemy ships, as you blow them away and anything that moves.
On the way collecting bonus weapons and power ups and energy.
At the end of each level, you meet the Boss.

Intense action, ultra smooth movement, pre-rendered 3d graphics, original music and amazing sound affects from the original full version CD-ROM I purchased.

Hope you enjoy it.
Any probs, let me know.

Thanks.
